{"tid":691092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"情緒激動離家失蹤 警尋25歲青年莫卓峰","createTime":"2018-06-05T11:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T16:32:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"020586afa05693bdac7abca44d5fc8a6a35c0f27","tid":691092,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T11:43:23.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】警方呼籲市民提供失蹤青年莫卓峰的消息。今日（5日）凌晨零時許，25歲的莫卓峰據報因事情緒激動，離開九龍塘地錦路2號又一村住所後，一直音訊全無，其家人指他沒有攜帶手機，擔心不已，於是報案。警方暫將案件列作「企圖自殺」處理，惟至今仍未尋獲莫卓峰，現呼籲市民提供相關資料。<br />\n<br />\n他身高約1.77米，體重約170磅，肥身材，蓄黑色短髮，圓面型，他最後露面時身穿綠色上衣、黑色短褲。警方呼籲任何人如曾見過或有莫卓峰的消息，請立即致電3661 8803與深水埗警署或任何一間警署聯絡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PJ3hkxQVgCUZ3GTchCJBPA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180605a100100.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FPJ3hkxQVgCUZ3GTchCJBPA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180605a100100.jpg&h=ed98e012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92%E6%BF%80%E5%8B%95%E9%9B%A2%E5%AE%B6%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4-%E8%AD%A6%E5%B0%8B25%E6%AD%B2%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%8E%AB%E5%8D%93%E5%B3%B0-020300946.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%25B7%2592%25E6%25BF%2580%25E5%258B%2595%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25B9%25A4-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25B0%258B25%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%258E%25AB%25E5%258D%2593%25E5%25B3%25B0-020300946.html&d=4nQmkFZQShaVZu8ftzY6Xdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=42984105\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92%E6%BF%80%E5%8B%95%E9%9B%A2%E5%AE%B6%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4-%E8%AD%A6%E5%B0%8B25%E6%AD%B2%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%8E%AB%E5%8D%93%E5%B3%B0-020300946.html</a>"},{"pid":"7e20f95d4d747dea362c168c0ef7fda28e33a2f9","tid":69109